  "description": "A wide shot of several large container ships and tankers sailing on a choppy sea. The largest ship, a massive container vessel filled with stacked shipping containers, dominates the right side of the frame. Its hull is painted a dark blue, and its superstructure is bright white. A second, smaller tanker is visible to the left of the container ship, appearing as a dark silhouette with a visible bridge structure. Further in the distance, a smaller ship is visible as a distant speck. The sea is gray and undulating, with visible wave patterns, and the sky is overcast with light clouds. The composition suggests a busy shipping lane or harbor.",
